	   <tr><td colspan=2>Totem,<br>I am returning for <b>my</b> city.  You'd best be gone by the time I get there, lest you find yourself in the same position as others who have failed me have found themselves:<br>endless days of pain and suffering mixed with semi-lucid rememberings of partial healings to draw out your torture are your fate when I get my claws in your skin.<br><br>Leave now, Grand Vizier, while you are able...<br><br>--Pusbag Infection<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Mon Dec 24 16:13:08 2001</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Emperor and Shamanic High Priest of the Trolls<br>"Worship Innoruuk, you worthless cattle!"<br></td></tr>
