	   <tr><td colspan=2>/ooc<br><br>Thank you.  This is particularly challenging, as there are something like four other writers putting together pieces of a much larger story.  I'm a firm believer that we should do nothing to damage each other's characters, but at the same token, should not make it seem as though we are invincible.  So, we need to write stories that tie in with the other authors' parts, without painting them into corners.  Not exactly easy, as I'm sure you can appreciate. :-)<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Arjaizen Izrhume<br>21st Circle Wizard of Erudin<br>Centurion Politico, 7th Legion</td></tr>
