<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=100896914628088></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f100896914628088><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=journal.html?user=2076&mid=100896914628088>*A secret missive to the Empress*</a> <a id=fs8 href=journal.html?user=2076&mid=100896914628088#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=21714><span id=Scholar>Totem</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>61 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Dec 21st 4:12 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>My Empress,<br>As I am certain you are aware, my lord Pusbag is enroute to you to secure his Empire by marriage.  <br><br>What I am about to state is of such importance and conniving that I have taken the utmost of precautions that this letter is not compromised by any means.  In fact, had anyone but you opened it, death would be immediate to the reader by magical poison and the letter itself would catch fire and disintigrate instantaniously.<br><br>I have been waiting for the proper time to leverage my position into a greater realm and have determined that that moment is now.  &quot;Emperor&quot; Pusbag has left himself open to treachery by his illfounded trust in me.  He has left me in command of all Trollen forces, the coffers, and the city.  The fool believes himself safe from harm and has thus exposed a chink in his otherwise formidible armor.<br><br>I propose that the guard he desires you to post at the wedding be instructed to seize him so that you may take command of all Evil.  This is my wedding gift to you:  a broken and emasculated Troll who wishes to be King.  My only request is that you give me total and complete control of Grobb and the surrounding countryside.  My borders will be Innothule Swamp-- all else is yours.  To make this happen I have corrupted his royal guard-- and upon a signal from you will not interfere with you taking action against their leige.  What you do with them afterwards is of no concern of mine.<br><br>You are probably asking just why would I do such a thing?  Why would I trade my position as Grand Vizier to the owner of the greatest Empire ever seen on the face of Norrath?  The reason stems from an episode years before where my brother was summarily killed by Pusbag and his friend, Unkk.  I got my retribution a long time ago with Unkk when I skinned him alive, I had to bide my time with Lord Pusbag.  For while I despise the very ground he walks on, I recognise the sheer animal cunning and ferocity which makes up his personality.  He has not left himself open to treachery in all the long years I have known him.<br><br>So.  The time is ripe for you to seize the reins of power from that pompous thug.  Will you aid me in my revenge?  The rewards are great for those who risk the most-- and the two of us risk a great deal in the switching of allegiances.  For you, no more sharing of power and playing second fiddle to a Troll.  For me, sweet revenge and my family's rightful claim of the Trollen throne.<br><br>Send word to me of your decision, Empress.  The guards await your signal!<br><br>Totem<br>&nbsp;<br>All hail King Totem!<br>/glares at everyone</td></tr>
