	   <tr><td colspan=2>Lord Totem,<br><br>Your missive comes at an inopportune time.  We were lead to believe that you were the most trusted of servants to Pusbag, and find your rebellious nature disturbing.  Surely you must realize that We hold the interests of the Iksar Empire foremost in Our thoughts, and rebellion of the sort you suggest does not seem to be in their interests.<br><br>However, your letter does pose some opportunity for Us.  From this moment forward, you are Our personal servant, Totem.  Fail to do Our bidding but once, and the letter you sent to Us will be revealed to Pusbag.  Surely, you do not wish to see this happen.<br><br>You will not find Us an overly demanding master, so fear not;  but always remember, your life is now in Our hands.  Failure, even once, will be your head.<br><br>/ooc on<br>Interesting new twist to the plot.  If anyone wishes to develops some of the twists further with me, my e-mail address is UsulaW@yahoo.com.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Dec 21 21:02:58 2001</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Usula Wurmbane-Infection<br>Iksar Necromancer<br>Empress of Fear</td></tr>
