<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=100899639040735></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f100899639040735><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=journal.html?user=2076&mid=100899639040735>RE: *A secret missive to the Empress*</a> <a id=fs8 href=journal.html?user=2076&mid=100899639040735#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=21714><span id=Scholar>Totem</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>61 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Dec 21st 11:46 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Empress,<br>Perhaps I do not make myself clear?  I <b>have</b> the keys to the city.  I <b>am</b> taking over Grobb.  What I am proposing is that you pick up the slack and take that which you intended to have anyhow.<br>/shrugs<br>I too, could pass along to Lord Pusbag this message demanding me to kowtow to you and expose your opportunistic manipulations, Queen.  <br>/looks slyly<br>What I think you may not perceive is that this is a prime chance to strike while the iron is hot, so to speak.  So I ask you again-- are you in?  Regardless, Grobb is mine.  Answer quickly, Empress, your Emperor shall soon arrive.<br><br>Totem<br><br>&nbsp;<br>All hail King Totem!<br>/glares at everyone</td></tr>
