	   <tr><td colspan=2>Word reaches Emperor Pusbag's ears that an Erudite was vandalizing his proclamations tacked up on trees in and around the area of Qeynos.<br>Pusbag's eyes narrow as he crooks a finger at waiting Troll.  He says something in a low voice to which the Troll then salutes his lord and hurries off to complete the task assigned to him.<br><br>As the Troll leaves the throne room, he signals to a small group of raiders to follow him.  They cast SoW and a Stamina spell on themselves and head off running towards the west.<br><br>--Pusbag Infection<br>&nbsp;<br>Emperor and Shamanic High Priest of the Trolls<br>"Worship Innoruuk, you worthless cattle!"<br></td></tr>
