	   <tr><td colspan=2>/OOC enabled<br><br>First of all, I just wanted to say that I love the roleplay that we are doing here. It;s fantastic. I know I fill up Pusbag's and Mugali's journal's with my pathetic posts. I would like to thank both of you for tolerating me.<br><br>Now here's the thing.<br>Recently, Verant created Firiona Vie as a &quot;roleplaying preferred&quot; server. I don't know if any of the wonderful roleplayers involved in this thread are currently playing on it, but I am planning on making a character on there and feeling it out. Looking at what Sony says about the server, it looks like a great and challenging twist on my favorite game.<br>I was wondering if anyone else would like to join me in this? It would be great fun to be able to roleplay with you all in &quot;person&quot; (to use the phrase VERY loosely) as well as on these boards. Now, I am not saying remake Lashara, and Judd, and Pusbag, yadda yadda yadda. New characters. New storyline. New fun.<br><br>What do you guys think?<br>&nbsp;<br>Lashara Dyran<br>Keeper of the wolves<br>Hand maiden of Tunare<br>Ranger of the 30th sun<br>Lanys T'Vyl</td></tr>
